tag-idolatry-shirk","tag-manners-adab","tag-monotheism-tawhid","tag-sadness-al-huzn","tag-sickness-al-marad","tag-supplication-al-dua"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8W2","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":1732,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/12\/05\/dua-depression-anxiety\/","url_meta":{"origin":34350,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Distress: Dua to say when anxious or depressed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 5, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas'ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA servant is not struck by worry or grief but let him say, \u2018O Allah, I am Your servant, the son of Your servant, the son of Your maidservant. My forelock is in Your hand,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39964,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/27\/dua-anxiety-depression\/","url_meta":{"origin":34350,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication against anxiety and depression","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 27, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNever is a servant struck by worry or grief but let him say, \u2018O Allah, I am Your servant, the son of Your servant, the son of Your maidservant. My forelock is in Your hand,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23969,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/11\/02\/hardship-pain-expiation\/","url_meta":{"origin":34350,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Trials: Every discomfort an expiation for sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNothing afflicts a Muslim of hardship, nor illness, nor anxiety, nor sorrow, nor harm, nor distress, nor even the pricking of a thorn, but that Allah will expiate his sins by it.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5641, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18509,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/14\/hardship-debt-shade-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34350,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Shade: Helping others in the shade of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 14, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Yasar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever would love to be shaded in the shade of Allah, let him help someone in hardship or waive a loan.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad\u00a015520 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0631\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26334,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/05\/13\/dua-complain-to-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34350,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Whoever complains to Allah, relief will come","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is afflicted by a pressing need and complains to people, his need will never be satisfied. Whoever is afflicted by a pressing need and complains to Allah, eventually Allah will provide for him, sooner\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41212,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/20\/allah-eases-depression\/","url_meta":{"origin":34350,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Allah eases our sadness as He wills","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, nothing is easy but what You make easy, for You ease the grief of whomever You will.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 974 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34350","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=34350"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34350\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=34350"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=34350"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=34350"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}